    Gv.The shortest path from (1,1) -> (3,3) is the following:Destroy cell (1, 2) in 2 seconds.Destroy cell (2, 2) in 1 second.Move right from cell (1, 1) to cell (1, 2) in 1 second.Move down from cell (1, 2) to cell (2, 2) in 1 second.Destroy cell (3, 2) in 22 seconds.Move down from cell (2, 2) to cell (3, 2) in 1 second.Move right from cell (3, 2) to cell (3, 3) in 1 second.Therefore the overall journey takes2 + 1 + 1 + 1 + 22 + 1 + 1 = 29seconds.

